description: If you attempt to reinstall or migrate an old copy of QuickBooks, you'll need to re-enter your license number and registration code during the install. If you have access to the QBL file your previous installation created, you can open it, copy the license and registration information contained within it, and enter that information as you complete your new installation.

common_filenames.description: license.qbl - A record of your Intuit QuickBooks licensing information.
